      "markdown": "| Grau | Dó (0♯) | Sol (1♯) | Ré (2♯) |\n|------|---------|----------|--------|\n| I | C7M | G7M | D7M |\n| ii | Dm7 | Am7 | Em7 |\n| iii | Em7 | Bm7 | F#m7 |\n| IV | F7M | C7M | G7M |\n| V | G7 | D7 | A7 |\n| vi | Am7 | Em7 | Bm7 |\n| vii° | Bm7(b5) | F#m7(b5) | C#m7(b5) |"
    },
